## How to Estimate Your CFO Budget by Revenue Stage

| Revenue Range | Monthly CFO Cost | Focus Areas |
|----------------|------------------|--------------|
| **< $2M** | $2K‚Äì$4K | Cash flow visibility, tax planning |
| **$2M‚Äì$5M** | $4K‚Äì$7K | Forecasting, KPI tracking, growth planning |
| **$5M‚Äì$10M** | $6K‚Äì$10K+ | Strategic planning, exit readiness, investor relations |

Your CFO investment should scale with your operational complexity, not just your revenue.

