## Expected ROI and Payback Period

Most companies see measurable financial improvements **within 3‚Äì6 months** of engaging CFO services.

### Margin Expansion
3‚Äì5% margin improvement = $150K‚Äì$250K additional profit on $5M revenue.  
Strategic CFOs refine pricing, identify inefficiencies, and optimize service profitability.

### Cash Flow Stabilization
Forecasting and working capital management extend runway **by 30‚Äì60%**, freeing capital for reinvestment.

### Valuation Uplift at Exit
Professionalized financials can increase valuations **by 20‚Äì40%**.  
Buyers pay premiums for organized, data-driven companies with clear growth trajectories.

