## Lowering Net Cost Through Tax Planning and Efficiency Wins

### Leveraged Tax Strategies
Integrated tax planning often saves **$50K‚Äì$200K annually**, offsetting or exceeding CFO service costs.  
Examples include entity optimization, R&D credits, and cost segregation studies.

### Real-Time KPI Corrections
Continuous monitoring reveals issues early‚Äîfixing a $10K/month leak before it becomes a $50K one.

### Reinvestment of Savings
Savings become growth fuel‚Äîfunding marketing, team expansion, or systems that compound ROI over time.

