## When to Hire (and When to Wait)

### Signs You‚Äôre Ready
- Revenue plateau with unclear next steps  
- Cash flow unpredictability  
- Planning major hires or new services  
- Repeated surprise tax bills  
- Preparing for exit within 3‚Äì5 years  

### Signals You Can Wait
- Under $500K revenue  
- Predictable operations and cash flow  
- Strong financial systems already in place  

### Phasing In Gradually
Start with a **specific project**‚Äîfinancial modeling, forecasting, or dashboarding‚Äîto test value before scaling up.

